When you create an account with thinkParity or you change your e-mail, a verification key is sent to your e-mail address and your account is placed in an inactive state. You cannot use all the features of thinkParity until you activate your account.

To activate your account: 
1 - Click the 'activate your account' link on the bottom left of thinkParity.
2 - In the dialog that appears, enter the verification key.